Package com.shouldis.bitset

Class ImmutableBitSet

java.lang.Object
com.shouldis.bitset.BitSet
com.shouldis.bitset.ImmutableBitSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public final class ImmutableBitSet
extends BitSet
Implementation of BitSet causing setWord(int, long), which controls all write operations, to throw an UnsupportedOperationException. Normal operations against the (protected visibility) array BitSet.words will still be able to modify ImmutableBitSets. The state of all bits are immutable once initialized.
Author:
Aaron Shouldis

BitSet, Serialized Form
